						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in front of the <hi rend="italic">chāvaḍi.</hi></p>						

						<p>Circa 12th century.</p>						

						<p>The extant portion gives the cyclic year Dundubhi, Kārttika ba. 14, the details being insufficient for verification.</p>						

						<p>It refers to a lady disciple (name lost) of the Jaina monk Harishēṇa of <hi rend="italic">Mūlasaṅgha</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Sēna-gaṇa.</hi> The epigraph is damaged.</p>						

						</summary>
